node_modules
*.tsbuildinfo
.vite
*.log

# NOTE: the build output is NOT ignored, and it is not here — vite writes it to
# `../src/serve/assets`, which is committed on purpose. `cargo install lait` must
# not need npm, and the published crate excludes this directory entirely, so the
# bundle has to live under `src/` and be in git. See docs/SERVE.md.
